# Project Structure

This is a pnpm monorepo workspace configured via [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml).

Key directories:
- **`src/`**: Contains the main web application source code (React frontend). See [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) for build config. File-based routing is used via `src/routes/`.
- **`worker/`**: Contains Cloudflare Worker source code (Hono backend, tRPC). See [wrangler.jsonc](mdc:wrangler.jsonc).
- **`packages/`**: Houses shared packages within the monorepo.
    - `packages/shared-types`: Contains shared TypeScript types, built to `dist/`. Configured by [packages/shared-types/tsconfig.json](mdc:packages/shared-types/tsconfig.json).
- **`remotion/`**: Contains Remotion video rendering configurations and components ([remotion.config.ts](mdc:remotion.config.ts)).
- **`alchemy/`**: Contains utilities, potentially related to AWS ([alchemy/tsconfig.json](mdc:alchemy/tsconfig.json)).
- **`remotion-proxy-function/`**: Contains code for a proxy function related to Remotion rendering ([remotion-proxy-function/tsconfig.json](mdc:remotion-proxy-function/tsconfig.json)).
